                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3835" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0085</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9254 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“买好”到“用好”：中航国际供应链服务模式的升级</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From “Buy Well” to “Use Well” : Upgrade of AVIC International  Holding Corporation’s Supply Chain Service Model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李晓辉，冯亮</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中航国际航空发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中航国际；供应链管理；设备采购；柔性生产；2019百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">AVIC INTL; Supply Chain Management; Equipment Purchasing; Flexible Production</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例叙述了中国航空技术国际控股有限公司（以下简称“中航国际”），在面对国外设备供应商产品价格偏高、售后服务不到位，国内航空制造客户需求增加，服务费降低的双重压力下，主动谋求业务转型升级，积极向供应链上下游探索，通过供应商管理、工艺提升、海外并购、线上线下等途径，开发形成一套“全寿命采购”体系，由为客户“买好”设备拓展到帮客户“用好”设备，从传统的代理进口服务商成功转型为能提供全面制造能力解决方案的集成供应商，完成了供应链服务模式的升级。本案例适用于《供应链管理》课程，使学生了解企业业务转型的过程，重点学习如何重构供应链各方的合作模式，如何对供应链上商流、资金流、物流、信息流进行整合。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In this case, we describe AVIC International Holding Corporation (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;AVIC INTL&quot;) , facing the high price of the products of foreign equipment suppliers and its poor after-sales service, the double pressure of increasing demand of domestic aviation manufacturing customers and reduction of the service fee,  actively seeking for business transformation and upgrading,  exploring the upstream and downstream of the value chain. By means of supplier management, process improvement, overseas mergers and acquisitions, online and offline methods and etc., AVIC INTL has cultivated a whole life purchasing system. Start from buying good equipment for the customers, then extending the service to make good use of the equipment, AVIC INTL has made a successful transition from traditional agent importer to integrated supplier with full-scale manufacturing capability solutions. The upgrade of the supply chain service mode has consolidated AVIC INTL’s leading position in this business area. This case is suitable for the courses of Supply Chain Management, so that students can understand the process of business transformation, and focus on how to reconstruct the cooperation mode of all parties in the supply chain, and how to integrate the business flow, capital flow, logistics and information flow in the supply chain.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链管理全局观、采购管理、供应商管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
